    March 2026

DESCRIPTION
***********
Abominable Asteroids is a 2D pygame clone of the classic Asteroids video game.

HOW TO PLAY
***********
Shoot and destroy all the asteroids to win. Catch supplies to get more ammunition or fuel.
Adjust the difficulty by changing the number of asteroids or supply drop frequency.
Give yourself unlimited fuel or ammunition for an easier time.

Movement - Arrow Keys or WASD
Select   - Enter
Shoot    - Space
Pause    - Escape

With a joystick use the D-Pad, Start, and bottom face button.

INSTALLATION
************
Option 1) Install on Steam

Option 2) Download an executable from itch.io.
          https://fractalfungusgames.itch.io/abominable-asteroids

Windows: extract and run the exe

Linux: navigate to your Downloads directory in a terminal and run the following

unzip abominable_asteroids_linux_x64.zip
cd abominable_asteroids
chmod +x abominable_asteroids
./abominable_asteroids

MacOS: 1) extract and drag 'Abominable_Asteroids.app' to Applications
       2) run it
       3) if prompted: Open 'System Settings' > Privacy & Security > click 'Open Anyway'

